T1  - Stock Market Declines and Liquidity
AU  - HAMEED, ALLAUDEEN
AU  - KANG, WENJIN
AU  - VISWANATHAN, S.
Y1  - 2010/02/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/02/01
