T1  - Time Variation in Liquidity: The Role of Market-Maker Inventories and Revenues
AU  - COMERTON-FORDE, CAROLE
AU  - HENDERSHOTT, TERRENCE
AU  - JONES, CHARLES M.
AU  - MOULTON, PAMELA C.
AU  - SEASHOLES, MARK S.
